50|$|The {{portrait}} of the king is almost exclusively known from his coinage. It is possible to identify several types of depiction in the coinage. He can be shown <b>with</b> <b>a</b> short <b>beard</b> and <b>a</b> diadem, but there are images which show him <b>with</b> <b>a</b> mid-length <b>beard</b> or <b>with</b> <b>a</b> long <b>beard,</b> still wearing the diadem. A completely different type of image shows him <b>with</b> <b>a</b> high domed tiara on his head.|$|R
